metadata.title: Latitude and Longitude Grid
metadata.description: Data Type: Base Maps;  This layer contains a latitude and longitude grid covering the Prince William Sound (PWS) - Copper River ecosystem. Additional grid data layers covering the PWS - Copper River ecosystem include a 1:250,000 scale USGS quadrangle coverage (quad250), a 1:63,360 scale USGS quadrangle coverage (quad63), a township boundary coverage (townships), and a section boundary coverage (sections).
